---
import ClerriLayout from '../../layouts/ClerriLayout.astro';
---
<ClerriLayout title="Website & Messaging" section="website">

<div class="page-head">
  <div class="page-eyebrow">11 · Brand & Conversion</div>
  <h1 class="page-title">Outcome-led, <em>not vendor-led.</em></h1>
  <p class="page-sub">The site needs rebuilding to embody customer outcomes. Replace vendor-led demo language. 45 → 15 minutes. Lead with what practices reclaim, not what we sell.</p>
</div>

<div class="page-body">

  <div class="progress-track"><div class="progress-fill" data-progress-fill="website"></div></div>
  <p class="mono" style="font-size:0.75rem;color:var(--muted)">Progress: <span data-progress-here="website">0 / 0</span></p>

  <div class="callout" style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:2rem">
    <div>
      <div class="lbl" style="color:rgba(207,252,120,0.7)">From</div>
      <p style="font-style:italic;font-size:1.15rem;line-height:1.4">"Join us for a 45-minute demo of our membership plan platform"</p>
      <p style="font-size:0.8rem;opacity:0.7;font-style:italic">Vendor-led product positioning</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <div class="lbl" style="color:var(--zest)">To</div>
      <p style="font-style:italic;font-size:1.15rem;line-height:1.4;color:var(--zest)">"15 minutes to take your practice back from insurance"</p>
      <p style="font-size:0.8rem;opacity:0.7;font-style:italic">Customer outcome positioning</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2>Site architecture priorities</h2>
  <div class="grid-2">
    <div class="card"><h4>Homepage</h4><p style="font-size:0.9rem">Outcome-led hero, category authority indicators (5,000+ practices, 7 of top 10 DSOs), social proof, multiple intent-based CTAs.</p></div>
    <div class="card"><h4>Solutions by audience</h4><p style="font-size:0.9rem">Independent practices, group practices, DSOs, employers (new SMB channel). Each with distinct messaging + proof.</p></div>
    <div class="card"><h4>Product pages</h4><p style="font-size:0.9rem">Platform, Bridge, API, University, Rewards. Outcome-led not feature-led ("Eliminate $3-6M in lifetime PPO write-offs").</p></div>
    <div class="card"><h4>Customer stories hub</h4><p style="font-size:0.9rem">Searchable by size, geography, outcome. Powered by AI case study workflow (D).</p></div>
    <div class="card"><h4>Patient-facing directory</h4><p style="font-size:0.9rem">"Find a Clerri practice near you" — geo + plan filter. Two-tier monetization.</p></div>
    <div class="card"><h4>Resources hub</h4><p style="font-size:0.9rem">Blog, ebooks, ROI calculators, market reports, webinar library. Canonical AEO content.</p></div>
    <div class="card"><h4>Partner center</h4><p style="font-size:0.9rem">Sunbit (payment plan), PMS integrations (HSO API Exchange, Open Dental, Planet DDS), employer channel.</p></div>
    <div class="card"><h4>Trust & compliance</h4><p style="font-size:0.9rem">DMPO, Knox-Keene, HIPAA, PCI — clear, accessible, enterprise-grade for DSO buyers.</p></div>
  </div>

  <h2>Conversion path redesign</h2>
  <div data-section="website">
    <label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="web-01-cta" data-section="website" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">Replace "Request a demo" with outcome-led CTAs ("See your practice's PPO write-off math", "Calculate your membership ROI")</div></div></label>
    <label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="web-02-entry-points" data-section="website" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">Multiple entry points by intent — learning / evaluating / ready-to-talk</div></div></label>
    <label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="web-03-self-serve" data-section="website" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">Self-serve resources for early-stage buyers (ROI calculator, plan design tool, assessment)</div></div></label>
    <label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="web-04-lead-magnets" data-section="website" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">Lead magnets by funnel stage — market reports (top), comparison sheets (mid), case studies (bottom)</div></div></label>
    <label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="web-05-segmentation" data-section="website" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">Clear separation: "I'm a dentist/owner" vs "I'm a patient"</div></div></label>
    <label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="web-06-50demo-test" data-section="website" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">Test "$50 demo incentive" with role/title segmentation (an open strategic question)</div></div></label>
    <label class="task"><input type="checkbox" data-track="web-07-rebuild-scope" data-section="website" /><div class="task-content"><div class="task-title">Decide: internal rebuild vs vendor (Verve Agency already designs Clerri assets — natural partner?)</div></div></label>
  </div>

  <div class="note-block">
    <div class="note-label">Website rebuild notes <span class="note-saved">✓ saved</span></div>
    <textarea data-note="website-notes" placeholder="Vendor evaluation, scope decisions, conversion baselines, A/B test plans..."></textarea>
  </div>

  <div class="topic-foot">
    <a href="/clerri/workflows"><span class="dir">← Prev</span><span class="name">10 · Workflow Recipes</span></a>
    <a href="/clerri/channels"><span class="dir">Next →</span><span class="name">12 · Channel Strategy</span></a>
  </div>

</div>
</ClerriLayout>
